init_text: Humans once wielded formidable magical power. But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect. When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They quickly find that force alone isn't enough to protect them from the new world they now live in.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They can walk among humans in society and no one is the wiser.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Humans are suspicious of each other and no one can be trusted.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Soon, the aliens begin to target humans and send them to "re-education" camps where they're brainwashed into service.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The humans need to figure out what's going on before everyone becomes an alien.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: If they can find a way to use the dogs to find the aliens, they may have a chance.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The humans who are able to keep a dog alive without it being killed or turning against them will be given a special status and allowed to live in the

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Every human is now desperate to keep their dog alive.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The humans who run the cities have their own agenda and are working with the aliens.
